   Here, at a glance, are key developments related
to President-elect George Bush's preparations for taking over as
chief executive:
   _On the eve of his return today to Washington, Bush had dinner at
a Florida beachfront vacation home with New Hampshire Gov. John
Sununu, a top campaign adviser mentioned as a candidate for White
House chief of staff.
   _Leaders of the Bush transition team said he wants to assemble
