<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Talk show host Oprah Winfrey has shed 67 pounds in
four months and fulfilled a desire to fit into size 10 jeans with a
liquid protein diet, plus jogging and counseling, she told her 20
million viewers Tuesday.
   Winfrey, 34, said her inspiration came from a friend's husband,
who lost 75 pounds in 12 weeks. She said she hasn't eaten any solid
food since July 7 _ with one notable exception.
   During a vacation to Hawaii with boyfriend Stedman Graham six
weeks into her diet, ``I became obsessed with having a cheeseburger.
I said if I don't have a cheeseburger, I'm going to die.''
   Winfrey said she ate the cheeseburger, then almost immediately
went out and ran a mile to burn off the extra calories.
