<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   When she married Burt Reynolds last April, Loni
Anderson says, she wed not only her ideal but her mother's.
   ``When I was a teen-ager in junior high school, Burt was starring
in the TV series `Dan August,' and my mother was so crazy about him
that she made us watch the show because he was her dream man. And
Burt does remind me very much of my father,'' the actress says in
the December issue of Redbook magazine.
   ``Then when I first came to Hollywood about 12 years ago, an
interviewer asked me who I thought the sexiest, most handsome man in
Hollywood was, and I said `Burt Reynolds,''' she says.
